## Vercel / local environment variables for Vite (React)
#
# For local development, you can keep these empty and rely on Vite proxy (/api -> localhost:5000).
# For production (Vercel), set these in Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables.
#
# Example Render backend URL:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com/api
# VITE_BACKEND_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com
#
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
VITE_BACKEND_URL=

